{
  "id": "card_n_0cd28a99c131",
  "kind": "note",
  "title": "Pirkei Avot §avot_05_13: There are four types of charity givers.",
  "body": "There are four types of charity givers. He who wishes to give, but that others should not give: his eye is evil to that which belongs to others; He who wishes that others should give, but that he himself should not give: his eye is evil towards that which is his own; He who desires that he himself should give, and that others should give: he is a pious man; He who desires that he himself should not give and that others too should not give: he is a wicked man.",
